  "detailed_description": "<strong>Test your skill while trying to unlock all ships by fighting on 6 unique maps full of different kind of enemies!</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>6 types of ships!</strong> Each with a different appearance, <strong>special ability</strong> and requirements to unlock! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349480/extras/4d3e9dc64aa20051f94ff12f8c41eb0f.webp?t=1770668125\" width=24 height=24 /></span><br></li><li><strong>6 types of maps!</strong> Each with different enemies, difficulty level, and visual appearance! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349480/extras/5ea12e033ddb0bb6661197b56796c233.webp?t=1770668125\" width=24 height=24 /></span><br></li><li><strong>Skill based gameplay!</strong> game is not that easy as it looks, you might need few tries to finish each map! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349480/extras/ef651bf1a2733dd1ce7aa99126591ec1.webp?t=1770668125\" width=24 height=24 /></span><br></li><li><strong>5 different buffs</strong> ready to help you through fighting! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349480/extras/818ac6d99ee8131fe35e24f6b342b59e.webp?t=1770668125\" width=24 height=24 /></span><br></li><li><strong>6 dynamic space-type soundtracks!</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349480/extras/842af11a44d907688c810efdd162d329.webp?t=1770668125\" width=24 height=24 /></span><br></li><li><strong>Mix of retro and modern sound effects!</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349480/extras/9099f22d04c81ca16271537583cd689d.webp?t=1770668125\" width=24 height=24 /></span></li></ul>",
